race.description: First National Real Estate Murray Bridge Stake Pr2
race.comment: BUSTING (5) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (22.91) last time out at Gawler. Has a strong record at this journey including seven wins. Rates highly and will give a great sight. KISSES FOR AMY (8) has been in the money at her last two runs, most recently when third beaten 1.5 lengths (17.53). Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from four starts. Bold showing expected. NO FINES (7) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing third (23.31) at Gawler in a Other over 400m. Must be included in calculations. REEL INFRARED (6) cannot be underestimated.
